Ekh '''prinjardi chhib''' si ekh [[chhib]] so si prinjardi palal zakono sar i mai zorali kai ekh [[stato]]. Butvar su i chhib le bareder [[sel]]esko andar o them. 

Kai varesave staturya si buteder prinjarde chhiba sar [[Afghanistan]], [[Boliviya]], [[Indiya (Bharat)]], [[Paraguay]] thai aver. Si vi staturya kai nai ni ekh prinjardi chhib sar [[Svedo]], [[Phandlo Thagaripen]], [[Phandle Staturya]], ama si ekh chhib mai zorali.

